Chris Greenwood and his family stayed at Camping La Chapelle in Argeles-sur-Mer with his wife and children . 
  The site is on the Mediterranean coast in the south-west of France . 
  The Greenwoods stayed at the site with their children Joe and Anna for 10 days . 
  Multiple swimming pools, a kids club, swings and a bakery kept the family busy . 
  The biggest selling point is the swimming pool complex . 
 